{"tid":1974720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國鍵盤戰絕對係香港革命既榜樣","createTime":"2020-04-16T04:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T05:29:40.000Z","uid":159697,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5e3f76c2438088db1f7654417554b9d1d22a99","tid":1974720,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"呢排追住睇泰幽默大戰小粉紅<br />\n大家食花生食唔少 笑又笑過 轉發memes<br />\n同時 大家又學到幾多呢？<br />\n<br />\n泰國人完美示範左點樣團結 槍頭對外<br />\n搞到啲小粉紅一棟都冇 twitter都唔敢入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">善用memes</span></strong></span><br />\n泰幽默識得用幽默手法 <br />\n好成功令到大部分人都關注呢件事 恥笑支那<br />\n啲圖傳播既速度又快又廣 <br />\n因為以幽默手法絕對比正統文宣勁 吸收呢類資訊既吸引力係大好多 相比係淨係追求資訊性同美感既文宣好好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">團結反支力量</span></strong></span><br />\n好清楚邊啲人係要結盟 成立左奶茶聯盟<br />\n將有反支情緒/同支那有過節既國家拉攏一齊<br />\n壯闊左成個氛圍 將支那係亞洲入面受到排斥孤立<br />\n<br />\n唔內鬥<br />\n唔分化<br />\n結盟更多同路人<br />\n壯闊反支聯盟<br />\n先係我地要做既野<br />\n<br />\n有時間鬥黃<br />\n不如學下泰國係鍵盤輿論戰係點樣玩<br />\n不如學下韓國係民主運動係幾咁團結"},{"pid":"1a2c058fcc370385526097c377763f9d578e9b1d","tid":1974720,"uid":159697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"啲memes好高質<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8LTWnC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8LTWnC.jpg&h=6e72e01a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBdKiAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBdKiAX.jpg&h=c749b537&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm1f9HD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm1f9HD.jpg&h=1a44a796&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdfd6ed8867cc45c4c13600382c76ec6774efc8d","tid":1974720,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGUtLga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2